title: Garmin MapSource Onroute Wandelkaart Netherlands v1.11
description:
Garmin OnRoute Wandelkaart Nederland v1.11 (Mapsource version)
especially for eTrex, GPSMap60 and Edge

Overview: This is the latest dutch Garmin GPS map made especially for excursions
(a "wandel" in dutch).
This map is fully routable compared to the non routable dutch TOPO map.

Manufacturer's homepage: <a href="
http://www.onroute.nl/wandel/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.onroute.nl/wandel/</a>

Install info:
Copy to C:GarminOnRoute and import wandelkaart.reg to the registry.
If you want to use different folder: edit wandelkaart.reg before importing!

Map Date: 13.02.2009

FID: 5140


Version 1.11 is specifically designed for eTrex, gpsmap60 and edge
devices. Devices such as Nuvi, Oregon, and Colorado are faster with image
building and have this 'light' version not needed.
If you have such a device it will build faster than you can use 1.11.
